Name: The Durka: You will (not) die
About the game: The Durka: You will (not) die is a visual novel based on such anime as Neon Genesis Evangelion, Death Note, Darling in the FranXX, Shiguang Dailiren. In this game, you play as a 14-year-old teenager named Mickey, who was chosen by one of the junior researchers of Live Corporation . But suddenly you have a very important role to play in saving humanity from Durka Corporation . But something goes wrong again, and you become a victim of some Mysterious person who wants something from you. Attention! We plan to make 4 chapters and a sequel called 'The End of Durka', but at the moment only the FIRST chapter is being developed.
